{"title":"hexo-notes","slug":"hexo-notes","date":"2020-02-18T13:06:51.602Z","updated":"2020-02-18T13:25:38.546Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-notes.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"hexo-笔记搭建\"><a href=\"#hexo-笔记搭建\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 笔记搭建\"></a>hexo 笔记搭建</h1><h2 id=\"环境安装\"><a href=\"#环境安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"环境安装\"></a>环境安装</h2><p>安装 <code>hexo</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"初始化项目\"><a href=\"#初始化项目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化项目\"></a>初始化项目</h2><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init hexo-notes</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd hexo-notes</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"更换-hexo-主题\"><a href=\"#更换-hexo-主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更换 hexo 主题\"></a>更换 <code>hexo</code> 主题</h2><p>下载主题</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git clone https:<span class=\"comment\">//github.com/HeskeyBaozi/hexo-theme-lite themes/lite</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>配置主题</p>\n<p>在 <code>_config.yml</code> 中找到 <code>theme</code> 配置项，将其设置为 <code>lite</code>：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">theme: lite</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"新建第一个笔记\"><a href=\"#新建第一个笔记\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"新建第一个笔记\"></a>新建第一个笔记</h2><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"string\">'node入门'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>编辑 <code>source/_posts/node入门.md</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"启动本地服务进行预览\"><a href=\"#启动本地服务进行预览\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动本地服务进行预览\"></a>启动本地服务进行预览</h2><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm run server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"将源码提交到-github-上\"><a href=\"#将源码提交到-github-上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将源码提交到 github 上\"></a>将源码提交到 <code>github</code> 上</h2><p>在 <code>github</code> 上创建一个 <code>hexo-notes</code> 的仓库，然后关联</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git init</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">git remote add origin https:<span class=\"comment\">//github.com/shealain/hexo-notes.git</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>提交文件到 <code>master</code> 分支</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git add .</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">git commit -m <span class=\"string\">'init project'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">git push origin master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"打包\"><a href=\"#打包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打包\"></a>打包</h2><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm run build</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>生成的静态文件放置到 <code>public</code> 文件夹中</p>\n<h2 id=\"部署\"><a href=\"#部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署\"></a>部署</h2><p>准备工作，需要下载关联 <code>git</code> 的插件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>修改部署配置，打开 <code>_config.yml</code>，找到 <code>deploy</code> 配置项</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">deploy:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  type: <span class=\"string\">'git'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  repo: https:<span class=\"comment\">//github.com/shealain/hexo-notes.git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  branch: [gh-pages]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>执行部署命令</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm run deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}